Title : Salloomt River
Text : The '''Salloomt River''' is a [[river]] in the [[Bella Coola Valley]] of the [[British Columbia Coast|Central Coast region]] of [[British Columbia]], [[Canada]].  It is a [[tributary]] of the [[Bella Coola River]], flowing southwest out of the southernmost [[Kitimat Ranges]] to meet that river just upstream from the community of [[Hagensborg]].<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/13627.html BC Names/GeoBC entry "Salloomt River"]</ref>

